### Variáveis
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api
@authToken = seu_token_aqui

### Registro de usuário
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### Criar domicílio
POST {{baseUrl}}/households
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Casa do João"
}

### Obter detalhes do domicílio
GET {{baseUrl}}/households/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Atualizar domicílio
PUT {{baseUrl}}/households/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "Nova Casa do João"
}

### Atualizar código de convite
POST {{baseUrl}}/households/1/refresh-invite
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Entrar em um domicílio
POST {{baseUrl}}/households/join
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "inviteCode": "codigo_de_convite_aqui"
} 